msgstr "- There is one girl. "

msgid ""
msgstr "One. "

msgid ""
msgstr "And she wants to have fun. "

msgid ""
msgstr ""
"- She can roll a ball, - color, - draw, - ride a bus, - play with the cat.Â "

msgid ""
msgstr "- She can walk the dogÂ "

msgid ""
